@startuml
title Create Process (Level 1) — VendNet

actor "Actor\n(Customer/Operator/Admin)" as User
participant "VendNet System" as System

User -> System: Request Creation with Data
activate System
System -> System: Validate & Process Request
alt Creation Successful
    System --> User: Display Success Confirmation
else Validation Failed / Error
    System --> User: Display Error Message
end
deactivate System
@enduml